nodes.text: Duke (male) or duchess (female) was a title of nobility. Misaani of the Anoat sector's Noble Court was a duke. During the reign of the pacifist New Mandalorian government, Satine Kryze ruled as the Duchess of the planet Mandalore. The Serennian Solha was as a duke. Rubix was a duke on the planet Shu-Torun. Blazor was a duke within the Black Sun.
